## Port Assignments

| Service | Port |
|---|---|
| PHP-MNGR UI | 4280 |
| PHP sites (auto-assigned) | 8100, 8101, 8102... |

---

## Why Cloudflare Tunnels?

T-Mobile 5G home internet uses **CGNAT** — your public IP is shared with many users and port forwarding is impossible. Cloudflare Tunnels punch through CGNAT by making an outbound connection from your machine to Cloudflare's edge. No inbound ports needed. Traffic flows:

```
Visitor → Cloudflare Edge → Encrypted Tunnel → Your Machine → PHP Container
```

Free, no port forwarding, automatic HTTPS, DDoS protection included.
